original_title: Palm Harbor Vice 2: Brotherhood of the Monkey
overview: In the sequel to Palm Harbor Vice, small town cops of Palm Harbor, Florida find their daily routine of setting up speed traps disrupted by a drug syndicate and a brilliant mad mad out to destroy life in their quiet community. If they're going to stop the crooks, the Vice cops must take part in a quest for law, order and a fresh box of donuts. This time with an alternate ending also.
tagline: In America's drug war, one police squad is all that stands between ruthless, merciless gangsters and the innocent citizens of Florida's Gulf Coast.
title: Palm Harbor Vice 2: Brotherhood of the Monkey
